      <li>
        <strong>Dark Energy</strong>: Not a mysterious fluid but a geometric consequence
        of discrete spacetime expansion
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Black Hole Entropy</strong>: Bekenstein-Hawking formula derived from
        lattice area counting
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Particle Masses</strong>: Mass as localized geometric deformation‚Äîcurvature
        concentration in the lattice
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Fourth Noether Law</strong>: Information conservation as the fourth
        fundamental conservation law
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Already Confirmed</h2>

    <div class="confirmation-box">
      <div class="confirmation-item">
        <span class="confirmation-icon">‚úì</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Gate Fidelity Scaling (2024)</strong>
          <p>
