        <div>
          <strong>Dark Energy Equation of State</strong>
          <p>
            Predicted w = -1 ¬± 0.03 from lattice geometry. DESI 2024 measurements:
            w = -0.99 ¬± 0.05, within predicted bounds.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Reading Guide</h2>

    <div class="reading-path">
      <a href={`${baseUrl}papers/main-paper-postulates/`} class="reading-step">
        <span class="step-number">1</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <strong>Start Here: Main Paper</strong>
          <p>The origin story and central thesis</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href={`${baseUrl}papers/unified-theory-diagram/`} class="reading-step">
        <span class="step-number">2</span>
        <div class="step-content">
